{"tid":720433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩男隧巴爭位開拖 同告受傷被捕","createTime":"2018-06-28T02:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T02:13:29.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e24fca704e3b4200023ec8d6c6ed8479c1d30a99","tid":720433,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"早上約6時39分，一輛由中環開往坪石九巴111號線隧道巴士，車上兩名男乘客，懷疑因爭位坐發生爭執，<span style=\"color: red;\">60歲姓韓男子先出手</span>，一拳打爆姓林(38歲)男子的鼻，林不甘示弱還擊，毆傷韓的頭部，其他乘客報警。<br />\n<br />\n巴士駛至九龍城太子道東近李求恩紀念中學附近，警方將巴士截停，經調查後兩男涉嫌公眾地方打架被捕，林鼻傷淌血，衣衫染血，與韓俱送院治理。"},{"pid":"45b195c1070096be5957bc988e9f2c5f95bce9ac","tid":720433,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/101329_c91e6ad251e313a4ecba3d4a7435fe50.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F101329_c91e6ad251e313a4ecba3d4a7435fe50.gif&h=16bb9715&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}